{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0020","text":"來頭這樣動聽 來源仍然未肯定","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","不確定"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["動聽","肯定"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,5,2,2,3,0,0,0,0,2,9,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["loi4","tau4","ze5","joeng6","dung6","ting1","loi4","jyun4","jing4","jin4","mei6","hang2","ding6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"來頭","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"這樣","pos":"DET"},{"text":"動聽","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"來源","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"仍然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"未","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"肯定","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"形容這段關係的開端聽起來很美好，但來源卻不確定，暗示著隱憂。"},"source":{"title":"所謂愛情","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3257","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0021","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0021","text":"何解會動情","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":5},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","困惑"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["動情"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ho4","gaai2","dung6","cing4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"何解","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"動情","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"疑問句，表達為何會對這樣一段不確定的關係產生感情。"},"source":{"title":"所謂愛情","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3257","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0020","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0022","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0022","text":"(仍然這樣任性 並沒耐性等你反應","structure":{"line_index":22,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","自我中心"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["任性","反應"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,2,2,4,2,2,2,4,9,5,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jin4","ze5","joeng6","jam6","sing3","bing6","mut6","noi6","sing3","dang2","nei5","faan2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"仍然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"這樣","pos":"DET"},{"text":"任性","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"並","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"沒","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"耐性","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"等","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"反應","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"括號內的補充，描述自己任性且沒有耐心等待對方的回應。"},"source":{"title":"所謂愛情","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3257","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0021","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0023","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0023","text":"自己先高興)","structure":{"line_index":23,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","自我中心"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["高興"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,9,3,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zi6","gei2","sin1","gou1","hing1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"自己","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"先","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"高興","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"}],"syntax_notes":"括號內的補充，強調自己先感到高興，突顯自我中心的特質。"},"source":{"title":"所謂愛情","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3257","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0022","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0024","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0024","text":"看見了結果也未結束","structure":{"line_index":24,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","執著"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["結果","結束"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,4,5,4,9,5,2,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hon3","gin3","liu5","git3","gwo2","jaa5","mei6","git3","cuk1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"看見","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"結果","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"未","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"結束","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"即使看到了結果（可能指對方已有對象或無意發展），仍未結束單戀的行為。"},"source":{"title":"所謂愛情","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3257","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0023","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0025","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0025","text":"你叫我退出也未退出","structure":{"line_index":25,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","執著"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["退出"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,5,4,3,5,2,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","giu3","ngo5","teoi3","ceot1","jaa5","mei6","teoi3","ceot1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"叫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"退出","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"未","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"退出","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"即使對方要求退出，自己也未曾真正退出，顯示單戀的固執。"},"source":{"title":"所謂愛情","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3257","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0024","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0026","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0026","text":"事事具備就是獨欠感情","structure":{"line_index":26,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","缺失"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["感情"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,2,2,2,2,2,4,9,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["si6","si6","geoi6","bei6","zau6","si6","duk6","him3","gam2","cing4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"事事","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"具備","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"就是","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"獨欠","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"感情","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"形容所有條件都具備，唯獨缺少了真正的感情，點出單戀的本質。"},"source":{"title":"所謂愛情","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3257","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0025","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0027","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0027","text":"還是這麼高興 情操更神聖","structure":{"line_index":27,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","自我滿足"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["高興","神聖"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,3,3,3,0,3,0,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["waan4","si6","ze5","mo1","gou1","hing1","cing4","cou1","san4","sing3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"還是","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"這麼","pos":"DET"},{"text":"高興","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"情操","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"更","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"神聖","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"儘管缺少感情，但仍然感到高興，甚至覺得這種情操更加神聖，昇華了單戀的行為。"},"source":{"title":"所謂愛情","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3257","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzI1Nw_0026","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
